        <title>Coal Ash Landfill Safety Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require the Administrator of the Environmental Protection Agency to review regulations for municipal solid waste landfills to determine if such regulations are, with the respect to the disposal of coal combustion residuals in such landfills, protective of health and the environment, and for other purposes.</title>
